#!/usr/bin/env ssc
---
name: effect-box
---

# effect-box — an imported effect, a generic effectful reader, and a handler

## effect

```scalascript
effect Box:
  def read(n: Int): List[Int]
```

## query — generic, folds over the effect result (mirrors a domain `query[S]`)

```scalascript
case class Acc[S](init: S, step: (S, Int) => S)

def query[S](n: Int, a: Acc[S]): S =
  Box.read(n).foldLeft(a.init)(a.step)
```

## runner — a deep handler

```scalascript
def runBox[A](body: () => A): A =
  handle { body() } {
    case Box.read(n, resume) => resume(List(1, 2, 3))
    case Return(x)           => x
  }
```
